<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Receiver on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/receiver/</link><description>Recent content in Receiver on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/receiver/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Ruby NoMethodError — Undefined Method Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/no-method-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/ruby/no-method-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="nomethoderror--undefined-method-fix"&gt;NoMethodError — Undefined Method Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;NoMethodError&lt;/code&gt; is raised when you call a method that doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist on an object. The error message tells you the method name, the receiver, and suggests similar methods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;NoMethodError&lt;/code&gt; is one of the most common Ruby errors. It means the object you&amp;rsquo;re calling a method on doesn&amp;rsquo;t have that method available in its current context.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Method doesn&amp;rsquo;t exist&lt;/strong&gt; — calling a method that isn&amp;rsquo;t defined.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wrong receiver&lt;/strong&gt; — calling an Array method on a String.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Missing include&lt;/strong&gt; — method defined in a module that isn&amp;rsquo;t included.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Private method called publicly&lt;/strong&gt; — method exists but isn&amp;rsquo;t accessible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nil receiver&lt;/strong&gt; — calling a method on nil (very common).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 1: Method doesn&amp;#39;t exist&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;push(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# NoMethodError: undefined method &amp;#39;push&amp;#39; for &amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;:String&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 2: Nil receiver&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# NoMethodError: undefined method &amp;#39;name&amp;#39; for nil:NilClass&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 3: Private method called publicly&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Secret&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hidden&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;secret&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Secret&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;new&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;hidden &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# NoMethodError: private method &amp;#39;hidden&amp;#39; called&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Cause 4: Missing module include&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt; Greeter
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Object.new.greet # NoMethodError — module not included&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="solutions"&gt;Solutions&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-check-if-the-method-exists"&gt;Fix 1: Check if the method exists&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;push(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# NoMethodError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct — use appropriate String method&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# &amp;#34;helloworld&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;concat(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34; world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# &amp;#34;hello world&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-handle-nil-with-safe-navigation"&gt;Fix 2: Handle nil with safe navigation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;nil&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# NoMethodError&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# nil (safe navigation operator)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Or provide a default&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;user&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;.&lt;/span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Anonymous&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-include-the-module"&gt;Fix 3: Include the module&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt; Greeter
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;greet&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Person&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;include&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Greeter&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Include the module&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Person&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;new&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;greet &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# &amp;#34;Hello!&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-call-private-methods-with-send"&gt;Fix 4: Call private methods with send&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Secret&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;private&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hidden&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;secret&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;end&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# If you must call a private method&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;Secret&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;new&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;send(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:hidden&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# &amp;#34;secret&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="name-error"&gt;NameError&lt;/a&gt; — undefined variable or constant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="type-error"&gt;TypeError&lt;/a&gt; — wrong object type for an operation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="argument-error"&gt;ArgumentError&lt;/a&gt; — wrong number of arguments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>